\import{table-macros}
\title{A TextMate bundle for Forester}
\author{liamoc}
\date{2026-03-07}
\p{As part of my embrace of well-designed old Mac software, I've started using [TextMate](https://macromates.com/textmate/) again. I made a bundle for building Forester forests that supports completion using \code{forester complete} (not LSP, as TextMate predates that).}
\p{The bundle can be downloaded from my [git repository on tangled](https://tangled.org/liamoc.net/forester.tmbundle).}
